<td>
<font color="#999999" size="1">Posted by: Langly on Sunday, February 23, 2003 - 05:52 PM CST <br><br></font>
<a class="pn-normal" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=index&amp;catid=&amp;topic=8"><img src="images/topics/eq.gif" border="0" Alt="eq" align="left" hspace="5" vspace="5"></a>
Halls of Honor<br />
Trial #1 - Rydda`Dar Dragon (NE crypt)<br />
5 clerics on 3-sec CH rotation.  Other clerics/druids spot heal from the AE.<br />
Use Bard singing MR/DR resists to help with AE's.  Start CH order on dragon MA once the trigger spawn enrages.<br />
<br />
Trial #2 - Alekson Garn (SE crypt)<br />
2 groups in each room, 3 rooms, and everyone else in main room killing Alekson Garn.  4sec CH rotaion on main room MA and other rooms keep MA's alive while rangers/druids kite wanderers.<br />
<br />
Trial #3 - Rhaliq Trell (NW crypt)<br />
Everyone get on middle carpet and just spot heal.<br />
<br />
HoHb - Mithaniel Marr<br />
Zone in and go invis to the left corridor. -310, +1200, +450.    Buff up and use fast heals until you get to MM.    use 6-7 clerics on 2sec rotation with all other healers using spot heals between rotations.
<br><br>
